(or even the original author after a few weeks) had to read the source
to figure out how to start the system.

This README covers:
- Project layout (backend + imis-frontend)
- Default seeded login credentials
- First-time setup on Windows (clone, npm install, npm run dev)
- How to log in (with the dev OTP shown in the alert)
- How to switch DB_DIALECT from sqlite to mysql later
